      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_procurement_002_special_equipment_bid_b021",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "简要规格描述或项目基本概况介绍、用途： 可开展全身各部位CT扫描，包括头、颈、胸、腹等部位的平扫和增强扫描，具备心脏分析软件包等高级临床应用",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_procurement_002_special_equipment_bid_b022",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "包名称： 激光扫描眼底成像系统",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_procurement_002_special_equipment_bid_b023",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "预算金额（元）： 1500000.00",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_procurement_002_special_equipment_bid_b024",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "简要规格描述或项目基本概况介绍、用途： 用于眼底视网膜及视网膜周边部摄影检查，支持超广角眼底照相、视网膜造影（FFA）、脉络膜造影（ICGA）等模式，支持疾病检测、诊断和分层分析，显示和存储眼底影像",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_procurement_002_special_equipment_bid_b025",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "合同履约期限： 包1：自合同签订生效之日起 180天内完成交付;包2：自合同签订生效之日起90天内完成交付;",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_procurement_002_special_equipment_bid_b026",
